            {
              "FullName": "DescriptionAttribute",
              "ConstructorArguments": [
                "Provides access to the global Sandbox.Internal.TypeLibrary for the current game context. <br/>The <code style=\"color: #DCDCDC; background-color: #111111; padding: 4px;\">TypeLibrary</code> is a runtime reflection system that describes types, their members, and relationships in the game and engine assemblies. It allows you to find and create types by name and id. It's basically a sandboxed version of the .net reflection system.<br/>"
