          "Documentation": {
            "Summary": "Provides access to the global <see cref=\"T:Sandbox.Internal.TypeLibrary\" /> for the current game context.\n<para>\nThe <c>TypeLibrary</c> is a runtime reflection system that describes types, their members, and relationships in the game and engine assemblies. It allows you to\nfind and create types by name and id. It's basically a sandboxed version of the .net reflection system.\n</para>"
          },
          "DocId": "P:Sandbox.Game.TypeLibrary"
        },
